These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, disco, pop
1. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | pop | disco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
City: hamburg, rome, miami
1. the person traveling to rome is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| City   | hamburg | rome | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, horror, western
1. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | western | horror |

