.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |    3    |
| Birthday   | october | march | july |

