.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, mango, papaya
1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
2. the person eating mango is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating pineapple is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | mango | papaya | pineapple |

 